                                                                                                                                                                        <p>
                                                                                                                                                                            <ol>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Cook some raw Ugthanki meat.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Obtain a bowl, a knife, an onion and a tomato.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Use the tomato and onion with the bowl while you have a knife in your inventory
                                                                                                                                                                                    to make a bowl of onion and tomatos.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Add cooked ugthanki meat to the bowl.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Mix flour and water to make pitta dough.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Cook the Pitta Dough on a stove to make Pitta Bread.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                                <li>Use pitta bread with the kebab mix to make a kebab.</li>
                                                                                                                                                                            </ol>
